<chapter id="chapter-configuration">
  <title>Configuration</title>

  <para>In order to use this project through Maven, use the following
  dependency:</para>

  <programlisting>&lt;dependency&gt;
    &lt;groupId&gt;org.geomajas.project&lt;/groupId&gt;
    &lt;artifactId&gt;geomajas-geometry&lt;/artifactId&gt;
    &lt;version&gt;1.0.0&lt;/version&gt;
&lt;/dependency&gt;</programlisting>

  <note>
    <para>For those not using Maven, this project depends on the Geomajas
    annotation project.</para>
  </note>
</chapter>
